{"tid":855702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］是龜也是頭　是龜頭也是賓周","createTime":"2018-10-10T08:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T08:12:53.000Z","uid":156635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42059159c2ffa75dc93b2b7c66533d3bf85bc710","tid":855702,"uid":156635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"是龜也是頭　是龜頭也是賓周 <br />\n撥開賓周　雜草幽幽　濃蓋著肉球<br />\n原野個個大龜頭　含撚逼於要深喉 <br />\n兩粒睪丸彈下彈下　彈到上月球 / 想一口食左碌鳩　唯有搭豉油<br />\n<br />\n是精也是蟲　是精蟲進入山窿 <br />\n掘開深淵掘出高峰　做隻快樂龍 <br />\n原野個個是精蟲　狂Ｊ車仔既雞容 <br />\n春宵一刻直不甩之　原野快樂龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0f740e49eddf769150a5a5165fedc21d40f5de","tid":855702,"uid":156635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}